Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在日本第一山富士山上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是要在山頂看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在向本八合目的山中小屋前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.33,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(560,430)}富士山 不可小覷…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山真的有啊 有種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 我也沒有現實感 好像身處在夢境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山頂上看的日出更加夢幻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要登上這種地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經算不上是路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵鏈只是一個引導 不可以抓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是空氣太稀薄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算待著不動呼吸也很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八合目 明明剛才起就一直看得見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候才能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事的 這點程度小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照自己的節奏走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢來 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 大家是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭好疼 我這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見大家的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 不要勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢來就好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 確實是累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為能更輕鬆一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很難走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭好疼 感覺非常的累 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點就到八合目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加一把勁 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十合目之前 有八合目和本八合目對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 要吃江米條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑糖也有哦 還有羊羹 其實還有綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺爺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我請工作人員刻了印 還有葵的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說這個山間小屋聖德太子來過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 還有歷史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖德太子 似乎是騎著能飛天的馬來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太子真厲害 葵 說是騎著馬來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個水壺似乎是200年前的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200年前是江戶時代？葵 是不是很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 心夏 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆先去預約過的本八合目的山間小屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是高山病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這先觀察下她的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒事的話 等下就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 我們先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走了 楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成兩個人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 明明那麼幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在向上面前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能拚命做現在能做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵沒事的 我們在本八合目等她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 葵 要喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭非常疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和心夏先出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為可以使用這裏的山中小屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在裏面躺著休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向她們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 完全沒有變好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當難登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是在走著 卻像在跑一樣上氣不接下氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然空氣很稀薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸就會好的 楓是這麼說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有口哨也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 平安到達了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵就交給我 吃了飯好好休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她沒事的話 半夜我們就向山頂出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是不用擔心 身體好了之後半夜就會出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃飯吧 肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me（不好意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}現在開始的話看日出是不是勉強趕得上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}你以為是誰的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多兩點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓緊的話 就趕不上去山頂看日出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 因為 我一直努力到這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是勉強自己再走下去 如果回不去了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山是不會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次都可以挑戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再穿一件比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是羊毛衫 很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都穿得好臃腫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多職業的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有外國人的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都爬到這裏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是楓發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說讓我們連葵的那份也要一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連葵的那份一起登山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和街上的黑完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是大自然的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}廁所募捐箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點太悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是葵也在看著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是銀河？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都想看的銀河 和我想像的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像斑點一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸很困難 但是情緒高漲 感覺不到疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空變得亮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 情緒高漲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點回去
